    "Background": {
      "text": "Characterized by proliferation of immature lymphoblast( >20% in periphery)\nLess than 20% of acute leukemias in adults,\nMost common form in children (see also\nLeukemia (Peds)\n)\nHighest incidence in 7th decade of life",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
