    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Lymphocytosis\n,\nneutropenia\n,\nanemia\n,\nthrombocytopenia\nLymphadenopathy\n,\nhepatosplenomegaly\nCNS and testes involvement common\nSymptomatic\nleukostasis and hyperleukocytosis\nare more common in AML than in ALL, CML, CLL\n[1]",
